<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Politis Auto Electrician</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #1f2731;
      background: #f3f6fb;
    }

    .content-wrap {
      width: min(1180px, 92%);
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .navbar {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #2d3561 100%);
      padding: 0.9rem 0;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    .nav-shell {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #007bff;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .nav-links {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      color: #ecf0f1;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      padding-bottom: 5px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: #eeff00;
      border-bottom-color: #007bff;
    }

    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a6bcb 0%, #0f4e94 50%, #1a1a2e 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 4rem 0;
      min-height: 52vh;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -50%;
      right: -10%;
      width: 500px;
      height: 500px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
    }

    .hero-layout {
      width: min(1180px, 92%);
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      align-items: stretch;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .hero-text {
      max-width: 760px;
      text-align: left;
      position: relative;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #bdc3c7;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    .hero-description {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      color: #ecf0f1;
    }

    .hero-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .booking-panel {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 1.2rem;
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 0.8rem;
    }

    .booking-panel h3 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .booking-panel p {
      color: #e8edf5;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .booking-panel ul {
      list-style: none;
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.45rem;
      color: #f5f8fc;
      font-size: 0.94rem;
    }

    .booking-panel li i {
      margin-right: 0.5rem;
      color: #00d4ff;
    }

    .btn {
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .primary-btn {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545 0%, #c82333 100%);
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.4);
    }

    .primary-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.6);
    }

    .secondary-btn {
      background-color: transparent;
      color: white;
      border: 2px solid #007bff;
    }

    .secondary-btn:hover {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.4);
    }

    .hero-image {
      flex: 1;
      text-align: center;
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: center;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .hero-image img {
      width: 45%;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    .offer-bar {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545 0%, #c82333 100%);
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.3);
    }

    section {
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }

    section > .section-inner {
      width: min(1180px, 92%);
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .section-heading {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .section-heading h2 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff 0%, #dc3545 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .service-grid, .review-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .card, .review-box {
      background: white;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      min-height: 280px;
      border-left: 4px solid transparent;
    }

    .card:hover, .review-box:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.02);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 25px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.25);
      border-left-color: #007bff;
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .card .price {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545 0%, #c82333 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .service-points {
      list-style: none;
      margin-top: 0.6rem;
      color: #52606f;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.35rem;
    }

    .service-points li::before {
      content: "•";
      color: #007bff;
      margin-right: 0.45rem;
    }

    .service-action {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #0056b3;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .service-action:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .quick-actions {
      margin-top: -1.5rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 3;
    }

    .quick-actions-grid {
      width: min(1180px, 92%);
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 0.9rem;
    }

    .quick-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(19, 35, 64, 0.12);
      border: 1px solid #e5ebf4;
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .quick-card h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }

    .quick-card p,
    .quick-card a {
      font-size: 0.94rem;
      color: #3c4a59;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .quick-card a {
      color: #0056b3;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .why-us {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f4ff 0%, #f0f9ff 100%);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .why-us .section-inner {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .why-text {
      flex: 1;
    }

    .why-text h2 {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .why-list {
      flex: 1;
    }

    .list-box p {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .contact {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #2d3561 100%);
      color: white;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
      border-radius: 16px;
      width: min(1180px, 92%);
      margin: 0 auto 3rem;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .contact-info {
      flex: 1;
    }

    .contact-details p {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .contact-form {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .contact-form input, .contact-form textarea {
      padding: 0.9rem;
      border: 2px solid #00d4ff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-family: inherit;
      background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .contact-form input:focus, .contact-form textarea:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: #dc3545;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.3);
    }

    footer {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a1a 0%, #1a1a2e 100%);
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .social-media {
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .social-media a {
      color: #ecf0f1;
      margin: 0 0.75rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 45px;
      height: 45px;
      background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .social-media a:hover {
      color: #007bff;
      background: rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.3);
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    .completed-services {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }

    .services-gallery {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .gallery-item {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
      border: 2px solid transparent;
    }

    .gallery-item:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.05);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 25px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.25);
      border-color: #007bff;
    }

    .gallery-item img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 250px;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }

    .gallery-item p {
      padding: 1.2rem;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero-layout {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero-text {
        text-align: center;
        max-width: unset;
      }

      .hero-buttons {
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .why-us,
      .contact {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .why-us .section-inner {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .navbar {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
        padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
      }

      .nav-shell {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .nav-links {
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      .hero-image {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .hero-image img {
        width: 80%;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .section-heading h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .contact {
        width: min(1180px, 96%);
        padding: 1.2rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="navbar">
    <div class="content-wrap nav-shell">
      <div class="logo">Politis Auto Electrician</div>
      <nav>
        <ul class="nav-links">
          <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
          <li><a href="#completed">Completed Work</a></li>
          <li><a href="#reviews">Reviews</a></li>
          <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="hero" id="home">
    <div class="hero-layout">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <p class="eyebrow">Trusted Local Mechanics</p>
        <h1>Expert Auto Electrical Services in the Bronx</h1>
        <p class="hero-description">
          Professional electrical diagnostics, honest pricing, and reliable repairs for local drivers.
          We keep your car's electrical system running safely and smoothly.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-buttons">
          <a href="#contact" class="btn primary-btn">Book an Appointment</a>
          <a href="tel:7189917044" class="btn secondary-btn">Call Now</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="booking-panel">
        <h3>Need Help Today?</h3>
        <p>Same-day diagnostic slots are often available. Call to confirm availability.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><i class="fas fa-phone"></i>(718) 991-7044</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-location-dot"></i>631 Tiffany St, Bronx, NY</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-clock"></i>Mon-Fri 8:00 AM - 5:00 PM</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn primary-btn">Request Service</a>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="quick-actions" aria-label="Quick contact information">
    <div class="quick-actions-grid">
      <div class="quick-card">
        <h3>Same-Day Diagnostics</h3>
        <p>Most electrical inspections are completed within 60-90 minutes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="quick-card">
        <h3>Transparent Estimates</h3>
        <p>We explain the issue first and provide pricing before any repair begins.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="quick-card">
        <h3>Warranty-Backed Repairs</h3>
        <p>Quality electrical work backed by a service warranty for peace of mind.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="quick-card">
        <h3>Fleet & Commercial Support</h3>
        <p>Reliable scheduling and fast turnaround for business and fleet vehicles.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="offer-bar">
    <p><strong>New Customer Special:</strong> Get 15% off your first electrical service!</p>
  </section>

  <section class="services" id="services">
    <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <p class="eyebrow">Our Services</p>
      <h2>Professional Electrical Services for Your Vehicle</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="service-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Electrical Diagnostics</h3>
        <p>We identify electrical problems quickly so you can get back on the road with confidence.</p>
        <ul class="service-points">
          <li>Computerized fault scanning</li>
          <li>Battery drain testing</li>
          <li>Detailed repair explanation</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="price">Starting at $79</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="service-action">Book this service</a>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Battery & Alternator Service</h3>
        <p>Battery replacements and alternator repairs to keep your vehicle running strong.</p>
        <ul class="service-points">
          <li>Battery load testing</li>
          <li>Alternator output check</li>
          <li>Charging system reset</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="price">Starting at $89</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="service-action">Book this service</a>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Wiring & Lighting</h3>
        <p>Complete wiring installations and lighting repairs for all vehicle models.</p>
        <ul class="service-points">
          <li>Headlight and taillight repairs</li>
          <li>Fuse and relay replacement</li>
          <li>Harness inspections</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="price">Starting at $59</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="service-action">Book this service</a>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Starter & Charging System</h3>
        <p>Expert starter motor repairs and complete charging system diagnostics.</p>
        <ul class="service-points">
          <li>Starter motor testing</li>
          <li>Voltage drop diagnostics</li>
          <li>Reliable part replacement</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="price">Starting at $99</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="service-action">Book this service</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="completed-services" id="completed">
    <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <p class="eyebrow">Our Completed Work</p>
      <h2>Electrical Services Gallery</h2>
      <p>See examples of quality electrical work we've completed for our customers.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="services-gallery">
      <div class="gallery-item">
        <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipNGbPBMFQUPnzLFtoHxMz9ABNumDepX1TXQYNfr=w243-h244-n-k-no-nu" alt="Electrical Service Completed">
        <p>Professional Electrical Installation</p>
      </div>

      <div class="gallery-item">
        <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipM46JUxTBJtHnNH7gVUwwcX5l3a6vJJFylU9F3I=w243-h304-n-k-no-nu" alt="Battery & Alternator Service">
        <p>Battery & Charging System Service</p>
      </div>

      <div class="gallery-item">
        <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipNDzpc2Y2VSZmgrN74Ik09ZZxuQABHwCbwZn379=w243-h304-n-k-no-nu" alt="Wiring & Electrical Repair">
        <p>Wiring & Electrical Repair</p>
      </div>

      <div class="gallery-item">
        <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/AHVAweqfoxbQU7Hexz5GE67MtEiYZSLZB09SvG2w2GkSCOD7k_b54R2aTFDRuDJJkbAoC04f_t8UEpyMcXFcxUqQe56NWJzYztIk9ND2fqpRdywKJ2XjVDfDXQNviRyOoEC37oI_usk1=w243-h304-n-k-no-nu" alt="Starter Motor Service">
        <p>Starter Motor & Ignition Repair</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="why-us">
    <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="why-text">
      <p class="eyebrow">Why Choose Us</p>
      <h2>Local Service You Can Trust</h2>
      <p>
        Politis Auto Electrician is built on strong community service, skilled electrical expertise,
        and dependable care. We focus on helping local drivers get quality electrical services
        without unnecessary stress.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="why-list">
      <div class="list-box">
        <p>✔ Honest pricing</p>
        <p>✔ Skilled local mechanics</p>
        <p>✔ Fast turnaround</p>
        <p>✔ Friendly customer service</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="reviews" id="reviews">
    <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <p class="eyebrow">Customer Reviews</p>
      <h2>What Local Drivers Say</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="review-grid">
      <div class="review-box">
        <p>"Politis Auto Electrician fixed my alternator perfectly. Honest pricing and great service!"</p>
        <span>- Maria G.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="review-box">
        <p>"I've been going to Politis for electrical work for years. Always professional and reliable."</p>
        <span>- John D.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="review-box">
        <p>"They fixed my car's electrical issues quickly. Highly recommend!"</p>
        <span>- Lisa R.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="review-box">
        <p>"Expert electricians who know their trade. Fixed my battery and starter like professionals."</p>
        <span>- Mike S.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="review-box">
        <p>"Politis is trustworthy and knowledgeable. Best auto electrician in the Bronx."</p>
        <span>- Sarah T.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="review-box">
        <p>"Professional electricians who care about their work and their customers."</p>
        <span>- David L.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact" id="contact">
    <div class="contact-info">
      <p class="eyebrow">Contact Us</p>
      <h2>Book Your Next Service</h2>
      <p>Ready to improve your car’s performance? Reach out today.</p>

      <div class="contact-details">
        <p><strong>Address:</strong> 631 Tiffany St, Bronx, NY 10474</p>
        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (718) 991-7044</p>
        <p><strong>Hours:</strong> Mon–Fri 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM | Sat 8:00 AM – 2:00 PM (Closed Sun)</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <form class="contact-form">
      <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" required />
      <input type="tel" placeholder="Your Phone Number" required />
      <textarea placeholder="How can we help with your vehicle?" rows="5" required></textarea>
      <button type="submit" class="btn primary-btn">Send Request</button>
    </form>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 Politis Auto Electrician. All rights reserved.</p>
    <div class="social-media">
      <a href="https://facebook.com" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
      <a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
      <a href="https://twitter.com" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
